Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.83,0:00:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Greetings, Tantabus. I am ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.54,0:00:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.96,0:00:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Luna's turning into\NNightmare Moon...again!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.18,0:00:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah? Well, we've got\Nthe cure for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.82,0:00:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! What is it doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.01,0:00:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,NO! It's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.92,0:01:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.97,0:01:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,My dream ended happily?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.56,0:01:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That cannot happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.11,0:01:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Regular by YayPonies\NWe have muffins!\Nhttp://yayponies.eu/
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.53,0:01:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh! This is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.45,0:01:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Rarity, thanks\Nfor setting all this up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.05,0:02:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,A grooming day for our pets\Nreally was a great idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.41,0:02:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my! Oh I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.31,0:02:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't get my normal\Nbeauty sleep last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.54,0:02:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I didn't\Nsleep well either.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.69,0:02:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm totally beat, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.43,0:02:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, Winona,\Ntime fer yer brushin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.30,0:02:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoops. I guess I'm too plumb\Ntuckered out to do this right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.15,0:02:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I even went to bed\Nearly last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.44,0:02:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But then I had a\Nreally scary nightmare.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.39,0:02:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.17,0:02:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, only, you know, I didn't\Nthink mine was THAT scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.58,0:02:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, mine sure was. There was\Nthis blue smoke monster and-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.29,0:02:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.19,0:03:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I dreamt about a blue\Nsmoke thingy too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.08,0:03:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.66,0:03:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So what? Probably\Njust a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.71,0:03:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That's an awfully\Nbig coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.16,0:03:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh. I wonder why I didn't\Nhave that nightmare.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.81,0:03:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I slept great!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.90,0:03:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So then what could have given\Nus all the same nightmare?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.29,0:03:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know. But I\Ndo know who might.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.09,0:03:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike, could you send a\Nscroll to Princess Luna?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.97,0:03:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.74,0:03:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,All set!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.81,0:03:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear Princess Luna. Last night,\Nmy friends and I all dreamt
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.60,0:03:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,of a creature made\Nof blue smoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.35,0:03:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you're very busy, but
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.03,0:03:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,when you have the chance,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.73,0:03:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,please let me know if you have\Nany idea what it could mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.98,0:03:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yours, Princess\NTwilight Sparkle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.25,0:03:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You can leave out the yawns.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.22,0:03:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Which of you saw the creature of\Nblue smoke in your nightmare?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.14,0:04:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! That was fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.61,0:04:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We all did.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.67,0:04:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Not me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.34,0:04:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh! We know!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.32,0:04:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So you've encountered\Nthe smoke monster, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.41,0:04:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The Tantubus is a\Ncreature of my nightmares!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.05,0:04:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It escaped from my\Nslumbers yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.64,0:04:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But, how did it get into ours?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.60,0:04:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The Tantabus is like a parasite.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.79,0:04:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,My dreams must no\Nlonger be enough for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.25,0:04:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it seeks others\Nto infect and corrupt.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.88,0:04:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It must have learned of you six\Nfrom seeing you in my dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.08,0:04:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa whoa whoa! So what\Nyou're saying is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.15,0:04:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You dreamt about all\Nof them and not me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.94,0:04:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So Smokey gave us bad\Ndreams. No biggie.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.49,0:04:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw that the Tantabus\Nhad grown more powerful,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.31,0:04:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,but I did not realize that\Npower was enough to enable it
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.03,0:04:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,to escape my dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.24,0:04:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,If its power grows,\Nit could very well
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.52,0:04:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,find a way to escape\Ninto the real world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.88,0:04:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It could turn all of Equestria\Ninto a living nightmare!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.99,0:05:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, OK, OK! I take it back. That\Ndoes sound bad! Really bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.51,0:05:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We've prepared everything
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.69,0:05:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,exactly as you requested.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.16,0:05:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Good. As you six slumber here,\NI will pursue the creature
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.84,0:05:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,into whichever of your\Ndreams it infests.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.19,0:05:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh! It'll be like a\Nprincess sleepover!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.66,0:05:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of Princesses, aren't\Nyou going to ask Celestia
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.90,0:05:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,for her help as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.39,0:05:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,There is nothing\Nmy sister can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.31,0:05:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,She has no power in\Nthe realm of sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.74,0:05:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Only I can move\Nfrom dream to dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.04,0:05:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I am afraid no pony\Ncan help me tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.65,0:05:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Even us?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.99,0:05:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.71,0:05:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You have all suffered\Nso much because of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.40,0:05:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You need only slumber
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.51,0:05:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,while I hunt the\NTantabus in your dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.45,0:05:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you said no pony\Ncan help, but I'm no pony.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.04,0:05:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to stay up and watch\Nover you guys just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.29,0:05:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.75,0:06:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,One good thing about not\Nsleeping well last night:
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.30,0:06:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,shouldn't be too hard\Nto fall asleep now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.56,0:06:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding?\NThis is so exciting,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.95,0:06:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how\NI'm ever going to -
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.94,0:06:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my! This is simply divine!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.00,0:06:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,How avant-garde!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.02,0:07:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget avant-garde. I should\Nhave said, "en-garde!"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.37,0:07:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.48,0:07:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You were such a\Npretty little chiffon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.71,0:07:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of monster\Nwould do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.62,0:07:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The Tantabus.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.90,0:07:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let's stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.46,0:07:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Please! I don't want you to\Nsuffer any more because of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.81,0:07:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I will catch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.33,0:07:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It has jumped into\Nanother dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.06,0:07:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I am sorry, but if\NI am to stop it,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.66,0:07:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I must follow it\Nwhere you cannot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.47,0:07:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.67,0:07:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall be able to\Nhandle things here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.99,0:07:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.93,0:07:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ La la la la ! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.30,0:07:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ La la la la la! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.97,0:08:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I followed the Tantabus\Nhere. Now I need only find--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.76,0:08:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry! Can't help it. An\Nidea pops into my head and--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.05,0:08:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oooh! Cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.58,0:08:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Eww! Cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.07,0:08:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.99,0:08:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.35,0:08:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Who wants ice cream?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.37,0:08:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmmm. It's so nice to\Nbe the pet for once.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.23,0:08:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,N-n-nice, giant, evil Angel?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.54,0:08:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Whew! Oh, thank you, Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.50,0:09:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, this is what I call\Nan incredible dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.54,0:09:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see the Tantabus has\Nalready turned your slumbers
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.94,0:09:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,into a nightmare!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.04,0:09:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.85,0:09:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my favorite dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.73,0:09:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ We are such happy flowers! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.18,0:10:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ We will now sing for hours! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.61,0:10:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Aren't we unbearably cute? ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.49,0:10:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ Watch me solo on jazz flute! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.17,0:10:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.50,0:10:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Luna!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.37,0:10:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened? Are you guys OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.53,0:10:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That...that was terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.03,0:10:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I...I never want to have\Nthat nightmare again!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.49,0:11:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Me either!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.30,0:11:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But Luna caught it? Didn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.09,0:11:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I am so sorry, my\Nfriends. I failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.13,0:11:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It will be back to infect your\Ndreams the next time you sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.00,0:11:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.51,0:11:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I reckon I could\Nlive without seeing
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.78,0:11:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,that thing ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.82,0:11:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But you will. Again\Nand again. Every night.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.13,0:11:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Until it grows powerful enough\Nto infect the waking world!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.61,0:11:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,After what I did\Nas Nightmare Moon,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.00,0:11:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,the fact that I am once again\Nresponsible for harming others
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.03,0:11:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,is more than I can bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.85,0:11:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be OK. Everypony\Nmakes mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.39,0:11:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as none of you\Ndreamt about another pony,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.95,0:11:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,the Tantabus remains\Nconfined to your dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.45,0:11:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I still have a chance to catch\Nit before it's too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.10,0:11:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Whew! That's good to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.35,0:11:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Although after you left,\NI did happen to dream
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.93,0:11:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I was eating a giant ice\Ncream cone with all of Ponyville
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.87,0:11:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,while taking a test\Nwe hadn't studied for.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.59,0:11:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,See, what did I tell ya?\NEverypony makes mistakes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.04,0:12:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But that means the Tantabus\Ncould be turning every dream
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.77,0:12:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,in Ponyville into a nightmare!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.79,0:12:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It is far worse than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.23,0:12:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Infecting all those dreams\Ngives it more and more power.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.62,0:12:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Soon it will be able to\Nescape into the real world
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.91,0:12:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and infect Equestria with\Nits nightmare plague!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.46,0:12:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you must let us help you\Nstop it before that happens!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.62,0:12:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But how? The Tantabus\Nwas able to escape Luna
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.68,0:12:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,when it only had SIX\Ndreams it could get to.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.32,0:12:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It is true. With so\Nmany dreams to hide in,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.47,0:12:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I do not know how\NI can catch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.81,0:12:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmmm. What if everypony in\NPonyville were having one dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.20,0:12:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I can create shared dreams, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.57,0:12:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But for so many ponies at once?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.78,0:12:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I have never done\Nanything like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.91,0:12:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The amount of power\Nit would take...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.10,0:12:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it is worth a try.\NIsn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.70,0:12:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course. I will do ing to end this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.45,0:12:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Including accept your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.28,0:12:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot allow the Tantabus to\Nescape into the real world.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.48,0:12:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,All of you must now\Ngo back to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.10,0:13:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And hope that I can\Ncreate such a dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.64,0:13:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Meow?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.98,0:13:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Mac! Boy, I'm glad to\Nsee something familiar!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.72,0:13:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Eeyup.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.64,0:14:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Ponies!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.83,0:14:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Luna!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.64,0:14:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no time for\Nbowing, my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.20,0:14:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,There is something coming!\NSomething terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.33,0:14:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,No! It is already here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.72,0:14:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I am so sorry. I brought this\Nupon you. But I will end it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.19,0:14:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess! What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.87,0:14:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It is taking all my strength
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.18,0:14:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,just to hold this\Nmassive dream together!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.62,0:14:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You will have to stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.35,0:14:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I truly wish I did not\Nhave to ask this of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.75,0:14:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you're in luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.12,0:14:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! We're already on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.42,0:15:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, I'll pay you anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.38,0:15:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Ya-wah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.23,0:15:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I got ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.73,0:15:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.77,0:15:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Mac! You can do anything\Nin a dream, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.75,0:15:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,E-wheeeeeee.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.83,0:16:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon! If that Tantabus\Nthing turns any more
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.46,0:16:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,of this dream against us,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.91,0:16:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll be too busy saving\Nponies to catch it
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.41,0:16:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and it'll grow powerful enough\Nto escape into the real world!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.59,0:16:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,How are we even gonna know\Nwhen it's able to escape?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.83,0:16:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I think we'll know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.61,0:16:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry, my friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.19,0:16:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What the--?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.69,0:16:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! We need your help, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.82,0:16:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy's right! We've\Nall got to work together
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.42,0:16:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,to stop it from escaping!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.31,0:16:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But how can we help? No pony\Nin Ponyville has your magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.28,0:16:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Or your speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.29,0:16:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.66,0:17:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,In Ponyville.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.66,0:17:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But this here isn't\NPonyville! It's a dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.06,0:17:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Eeyup!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.32,0:17:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And not just any.\NThis is YOUR dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.22,0:17:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything you can do in your\Ndreams, you can do now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.16,0:17:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if you're gonna dream,\Nmight as well dream big, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.60,0:17:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,He-ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.02,0:17:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,MEOW!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.17,0:18:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's working!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.71,0:18:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's not enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.87,0:18:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Then do more! This\Nis a dream, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.47,0:18:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot hold this\Ndream together much longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.39,0:18:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Equestria will\Nfall because of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.61,0:18:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I crazy or did it\Njust get even bigger
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.01,0:18:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,after Luna said that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.40,0:19:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's feeding off\Nyour guilt, Princess Luna!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.54,0:19:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,If that is so, then perhaps that\Nis how it grew strong enough
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.30,0:19:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,to escape in the first place!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.23,0:19:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Say what now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.97,0:19:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I created the Tantabus
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.28,0:19:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,to give myself the same\Nnightmare every night.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.95,0:19:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,To punish myself for the evil\NI caused as Nightmare Moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.01,0:19:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But why would you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.59,0:19:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,To make sure I\Nnever forgave myself
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.56,0:19:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,for how much Equestria\Nsuffered because of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.41,0:19:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But it seems I have\Nnot learned my lesson,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.77,0:19:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,for now I have only\Nmade you suffer more!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.88,0:19:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But that means you might just be\Nthe key to stopping all this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.21,0:19:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! If it gets strong\Nbecause you feel bad
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.02,0:19:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,about what you did\Nas Nightmare Moon,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.35,0:19:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,then you just gotta stop\Nfeeling bad for what you did!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.95,0:19:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,How can I forgive myself? I am\Nno better now than I was then!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.35,0:19:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,My creation is about to turn the\Nworld into a living nightmare!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.43,0:20:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But look at what YOU'RE doing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.34,0:20:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Nightmare Moon would\Nhave wanted the Tantabus
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.35,0:20:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,to turn Equestria\Ninto a nightmare.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.84,0:20:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You're doing everything\Nyou can to stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.34,0:20:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.62,0:20:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That proves you're not the same\Npony you were then!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.86,0:20:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Everypony who knows you\Nknows that Nightmare Moon
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.12,0:20:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,is in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.39,0:20:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We all trust you, Luna.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.54,0:20:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you trust us enough\Nto believe we're right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.99,0:20:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.21,0:20:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. Thank you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.60,0:20:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Luna did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.99,0:21:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,She sure did! Only, I'm not\Nexactly sure WHAT she did.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.98,0:21:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Luna created the Tantabus\Nto punish herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.74,0:21:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The worse she felt,\Nthe more power it had.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.60,0:21:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But once she finally\Nforgave herself
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.56,0:21:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,for what Nightmare Moon did...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.17,0:21:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Poof!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.97,0:21:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Shhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.74,0:21:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh. Wonder what she's\Ndreaming about now?
